<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />光是改變一件家具擺設，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就能讓人對房間的印象大大改觀呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看得出這裡充滿了你的品味，<delay20 />
是很棒的房間喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="002" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不太知道該怎麼形容才好<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過感覺你的房間<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />相當簡潔優雅呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="003" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00">我現在<delay20 /><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />正熱衷於研究「看得見收納法」呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />請讓我參考參考你家的室內裝潢，<delay8 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />還有居家擺設吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="004" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像這樣子在家裡悠閒地聊天，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />感覺連我們兩個人內心的距離
都縮短了呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="005" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說家會反映出居住者的性格，<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />原來這種說法是真的呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為我光是待在你房間，<delay20 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就覺得心情變得像跟你聊天時<delay20 />
一樣開心喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="006" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />只要待在<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的房間，<delay20 />
<anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />就覺得整個人的精神都煥然一新了！<10_4 />
<anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />簡直就像能量景點一樣呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="007" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />因為<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />的房間<delay20 />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />待起來很舒服，<delay20 />
所以不管來玩幾次都不會膩呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />果然房間能不能<delay20 />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />布置得讓人感到放鬆，<delay8 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才是最重要的關鍵吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="008" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><tag a="110" b="4" />，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hello" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你也很常來<delay8 />
<tag a="115" b="1" arg="0xcd00" /><tag a="110" b="13" />家玩嗎？<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="101_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="QuestionMark" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你打算要在這個房間放什麼呢？<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />呵呵，<delay8 />一想到該怎麼布置，<delay8 />
我就覺得好期待喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你的生活真是簡約，完全沒有多餘的物品呢。<delay frames="40" />
<tag a="110" b="0" /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然這麼說，<delay8 />但你的房間這麼空，
已經超越簡約的境界了吧，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="101_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">你這裡連一件家具都還沒布置呢。<10_4 />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過思考要擺什麼家具的時間，<delay8 />
其實才是最開心的喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>